subsection_content:
Back acne refers to acne that forms and develops on the back, mainly the upper back, sometimes even on the arms. Just like acne on many other places on the body, acne on the back can be blackheads, whiteheads, skin tags or cysts. (first)
Back acne can include many different types of acne
